obsv_mat          Scilab Group          Scilab Function            obsv_mat
NAME
   obsv_mat - observability matrix
  
CALLING SEQUENCE
 [O]=obsv_mat(A,C)
 [O]=obsv_mat(sl)
PARAMETERS
 A,C,O      : real matrices
            
 sl         : syslin list
            
DESCRIPTION
   obsv_mat returns the observability matrix:
  
 O=[C; CA; CA^2;...; CA^(n-1) ]
SEE ALSO
   contrss, obsvss, obs_gram 
  
